        with ease and interactivity. It is designed with robust authentication, role-based permissions, interactive map 
        features, and smooth image uploading—all aimed at delivering a seamless and intuitive user experience.
    </p>
    <ul class="sn-list">
      <li>MongoDB, Express.js, Node.js, EJS, HTML/CSS/JavaScript</li>
      <li>Passport.js for secure user authentication</li>
      <li>Cloudinary for image storage</li>
      <li>Mapbox for geolocation and interactive maps</li>
      <li>Joi for schema validation, and layered error handling</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="sn-text">
      StayNest is currently deployed on Render and publicly accessible via GitHub.
